snippet.title: Taiko no Tatsujin: Drum 'n' Fun! - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
For the first time in Europe, the smash-hit rhythm games Taiko no Tatsujin: Drum ‘n’ Fun! for Nintendo Switch and Taiko no Tatsujin: Drum Session! for PS4 are now available! Ready to drum up some fun?! 🥁 🎵
Get your copy: https://fcld.ly/tnt
